324
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,200
You left a handprint.

325
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,590
How arrogant.

326
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:30,310
Today,

327
00:17:30,830 --> 00:17:32,550
