337
00:18:27,310 --> 00:18:29,790
Where's the new substitute who
will be making medicine for me?

338
00:18:30,550 --> 00:18:32,200
He's here.

339
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:41,960
Sorry.

340
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:45,310
Sorry, child.

341
