374
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:02,750
Let go!

375
00:21:03,110 --> 00:21:04,110
Let go!

376
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:05,920
Yes.

377
00:22:06,350 --> 00:22:07,247
Yes.

378
00:22:07,271 --> 00:22:08,326
That's right!

379
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:09,247
That's right!

380
00:22:09,271 --> 00:22:10,830
That's right!

381
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:19,350
See that?

382
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:22,960
This is the law of survival in this world.

383
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:25,200
Only by taking revenge

384
00:22:25,270 --> 00:22:27,350
