399
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:27,680
Everyone in Shouhua Academy
feels tired and demoralized.

400
00:23:27,681 --> 00:23:47,935
Officail Website : Kissasia.ID  Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

401
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:28,960
I figured

402
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,550
