is incapable of leading her warriors...

413
00:23:55,550 --> 00:23:57,110
Father has been sleeping for many days.

414
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:59,590
Lord Hanfeng, how did you obtain

415
00:23:59,790 --> 00:24:02,790
