the Shouhua Academy.

468
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:17,160
All right.

469
00:26:18,050 --> 00:26:19,050
All right, now.

470
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:23,400
With my cultivation,

471
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,830
