through the Perfected Stage.

487
00:27:13,550 --> 00:27:15,750
Immortal Ji has been
working hard to achieve this.

488
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,936
It's hard to obtain the Perfected Stage.

489
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,006
Immortal Ji only needs a bit more

490
00:27:19,030 --> 00:27:20,070
