520
00:28:08,031 --> 00:28:09,351
Help me take a look, Immortal Ji.

521
00:28:09,790 --> 00:28:10,790
Immortal Ji.

522
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:12,696
Immortal Ji, my cultivation
has been stagnant.

523
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:13,347
What should I do?

524
00:28:13,371 --> 00:28:14,416
- Help me take a look.
- Immortal Ji.

525
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:16,270
- Help me take a look.
- Everyone, make way.

526
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:20,000
Help me take a look.

527
