538
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,110
Netherbeast-Luring Caltrop?

539
00:29:16,310 --> 00:29:17,390
Netherbeast-Luring Caltrop?

540
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:19,066
Netherbeast-Luring Caltrop?

541
00:29:19,090 --> 00:29:20,090
